                                Government Office Hours and Holidays

                                                                    [_blnk.gif]
   [_blnk.gif]

   Operating hours for most Yadkin County Local Government offices
   are 8:00 a.m.-- 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday.
   Emergency services are available 24-hours-a-day, seven days a week.
   [_blnk.gif]
   [_blnk.gif]

   Holiday closings will be observed for calendar year 2001 as follows:
     * New Year's Day
     ML King Jr.'s Birthday
     * Good Friday
     * Memorial Day
     * Independence Day
     * Labor Day
     * Veteran's Day
     * Thanksgiving
     * Christmas

   In the event local government offices are closed due to inclement
   weather, emergencies,
   technical related problems, or normal holiday closings, such
   information will be announced here.
   [_blnk.gif]
   [_blnk.gif]


